    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DEMIURGOS: 夺取神性</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《造物主》中，你化身为马尔杜克、洛基、阿努比斯、战神或波塞冬等神灵，与其他神祇围绕宇宙棋盘展开激烈竞争，由神秘的造物主主持。你将在一个充满凡人棋子的动态活体棋盘上战斗，目标是通过独特且富有挑战性的条件击败敌神，赢得独占的天皇称号——胜利点。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>宇宙棋盘竞技场</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >化身一位神祇，围绕宇宙棋盘与其他神灵竞技，活体棋盘是一个充满生机的动态世界，由造物主指引。施展奇迹、管理信仰，在可暂停的实时世界中平衡深思熟虑的策略与神圣的紧急行动，掌控全局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2229910/extras/c7d2edadf55db9293524b2fb1114b998.webp?t=1771626642\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2229910/extras/c7d2edadf55db9293524b2fb1114b998.poster.webp?t=1771626642\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=250 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>独特的神力</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每位神灵拥有独特的能力与神圣特权，带来截然不同的玩法风格。你可以选择成为仁慈的光明之神，或混乱的黑暗之神，用你的战略与传奇塑造属于你的神圣道路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2229910/extras/2732939053a25f5c1ebfbee18ef8cf12.webp?t=1771626642\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2229910/extras/2732939053a25f5c1ebfbee18ef8cf12.poster.webp?t=1771626642\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=250 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>打造你的宗教</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >倾听你的信徒，解决他们的诉求以增强他们的虔诚。指挥你的祭司，将他们升级为不同类型的高级祭司，并通过选择不同的教义来定制你的宗教，塑造其信仰与文化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2229910/extras/a3344d53009da6bdfdf095064a9ac72b.webp?t=1771626642\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2229910/extras/a3344d53009da6bdfdf095064a9ac72b.poster.webp?t=1771626642\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=250 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>重塑世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >运用强大的奇迹改造地形，创造符合你神圣意志的生态系统，让世界成为你权力的延伸。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2229910/extras/1a611a33205828048dc2b108e8b907fe.webp?t=1771626642\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2229910/extras/1a611a33205828048dc2b108e8b907fe.poster.webp?t=1771626642\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=250 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>神对神竞争</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与敌对神祇进行直接或间接的对抗，支持多人对战，带来史诗般的对决。通过独特且挑战性的条件赢得独占的胜利点——每个天皇称号只能由一位神持有，竞争异常激烈。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2229910/extras/6da79721931cd017a9ed641259e0e9fc.avif?t=1771626642\" width=616 height=356 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>未来扩展</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过计划中的DLC和更新，扩展你的神灵阵容，解锁新的神祇与独特能力，丰富你的游戏体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>开发中版本</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《造物主》目前处于活跃开发阶段，包含临时美术资源和实验性玩法，仍在不断完善。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>限量访问</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《造物主》的访问目前仅限于通过测试者朋友的邀请。加入我们的Discord社区以获取更多信息和参与机会。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2229910/extras/03b0faa2faaa25772643058f0acbf647.avif?t=1771626642\" width=600 height=64 /></span></p>",
